window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>From <i>New York Times</i> best-selling author Carrie Ann Ryan comes a new romance in her Montgomery Ink series… </p> <p>Tattoo artist Brandon never thought he'd see her again. He'd trained himself never to think of her or what they'd had together. It was the only way he'd been able to survive, but now she's standing right in front of him and he can hardly breathe. Lauren hadn't known he'd be part of her plans until it was too late. She'd thought he was gone from her life and memories forever. Now he's in her orbit once more and she'll have to fight to remember the girl she once was and the woman she's become.</p>"; 
